snippet.title: Δ & ♫ Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Just Shapes & Beats, the game about shapes, and beats. Once nominated for the most self explanatory game title of all time, didn't win.

Coming to Steam and Nintendo Switch May 31st 2018... finally!

Website: www.justshapesandbeats.com
Steam: www.steam.justshapesandbeats.com
eshop: www.switch.justshapesandbeats.com
Spotify: bit.ly/jsbost

Trailer tracks:
Sabrepulse - Termination Shock (https://sabrepulse.bandcamp.com/)
Noisestorm - Barracuda  (http://music.monstercat.com/track/barracuda)
PIXL - Sugar Rush (http://music.monstercat.com/album/sugar-rush-ep)
Nitro Fun - New Game (http://music.monstercat.com/track/new-game)
Plesco - Unlocked (https://wolfbeatsofficial.bandcamp.com/track/unlocked)

ESRB 10
